    "description": "Everything is kinda ruined, so good luck or something. In Crupt, each Wave will present you with a new enemy to fight and a different building to restore. With every Wave you conquer, you'll expand your arsenal along with your social circle as you try to bring back everyone and everything.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 Waves with a new enemy to accompany each Wave<br></li><li>A big boss thing every 5 Waves<br></li><li>A building (or part of a building) to repair each Wave<br></li><li>A new wacky character to talk to for every building repaired<br></li><li>Resource management elements let you experience the wonders of semi-passive income<br></li><li>Like 50 Items to buy<br></li><li>Post-game content<br></li><li>Achievements, if you're into that sorta thing<br></li><li>Original soundtrack and (mostly) cute pixel art graphics<br></li><li>Meet?<br></li><li>Plenty of Bundles<br></li><li>Chups, Flumps, Squmps, and even Lubs</li></ul>",
